  "title": "Belgic Art. 16: Eternal Election",
  "body": "We believe that, all the posterity of Adam being thus fallen into perdition by the sin of our first parents, God then did manifest himself such as he is — that is to say, merciful and just: merciful, since he delivers from this perdition all those whom he has elected; and just, in leaving the others in their fall.",
